33
00:03:42,411 --> 00:03:46,411
seperti yang sering kita lihat di novel atau film!

34
00:03:46,411 --> 00:03:49,311
Tapi, guru...

35
00:03:49,311 --> 00:03:51,611
Kenapa kau ada di sini?

36
00:03:51,611 --> 00:03:54,511
Kamarku ada di sebelah kamar Tn. Takai.

37
00:03:54,511 --> 00:03:56,911
Oh, benarkah?

38
00:03:56,911 --> 00:03:59,411
Mereka berdua baru saja datang mengunjungi aku.

39
00:03:59,411 --> 00:04:02,811
