Tokyo. Aku di Tokyo!

114
00:07:32,111 --> 00:07:33,711
Apa? Tokyo!

115
00:07:33,711 --> 00:07:35,211
Oh, yah, itu benar.

116
00:07:35,211 --> 00:07:36,511
Aku tadinya akan pergi kembali menemuimu

117
00:07:36,511 --> 00:07:38,511
